ALSA CONF README
~~~~~~~~~~~

update-asound-conf.sh

[cols=">s,6a",frame="topbot",options="header"]
|====================================================================
|Name | Description

| Summary |
Select a proper sound card for asound.conf

| Automated |
YES

| Kernel Config Option |
CONFIG_SND

| Software Dependency |
aplay is installed in rootfs

| Non-default Hardware Configuration |
N/A

| Test Procedure |
. Run:

 /unit_tests/Audio# ./update-asound-conf.sh

| Expected Result |
The /etc/asound.conf is updated

|====================================================================

